definition: to prepare/get ready/to provide or equip

sentences.english: Bedding is not provided, so bring a sleeping bag.
sentences.chinese: 不提供臥具，所以得自備睡袋。
可接納50人左右團隊，自備停車場。

sentences.english: Please bring along a bottle of water.
sentences.chinese: 請每位同學自備水一壼。

sentences.english: Participants should bring their own sticks, mouth guard, shin pads.
sentences.chinese: 參加者需要自備球棍，牙箍，護脛。

sentences.english: If you are self-provided please tell us.
sentences.chinese: 如果您自備請告訴我們。

sentences.english: Has a large indoor pool, owned crane several, stock sufficient inventory.
sentences.chinese: 建有大型室內庫，自備吊車數臺，現貨庫存充足。

sentences.english: I am only looking to gather the information below for Certified Used or Certified Pre-Owned vehicles.
sentences.chinese: 我只是希望收集以下認證或認證前用自備車輛的信息。

sentences.english: At some restaurant, you can take to go into self-provided wine.
sentences.chinese: 在有些餐館，你可以帶入自備酒。

sentences.english: If you need to use a computer, it is suggested to bring your own laptop and internet cable here.
sentences.chinese: 如需使用電腦，請自備個人手提電腦及網路線。

sentences.english: That triggered the emergency diesel generators to startup and provide backup power for plant systems.
sentences.chinese: 由此工廠自備緊急柴油發電機啓動爲工廠提供電力。

sentences.english: Bring ear plugs if you are a light sleeper or sensitive to snoring.
sentences.chinese: 如果你淺睡易醒或是對鼾聲敏感，請自備耳塞。

sentences.english: Students should use their own padlocks to secure the lockers during the locker rental period.
sentences.chinese: 學生在租借期間必須自備扣鎖把儲物箱鎖好。

sentences.english: Who serves as a soldier at his own expense?
Please bring your own laptop and a toy car.
sentences.chinese: 請自備筆記本和一臺玩具車。

sentences.english: If only I had a car of my own. I could drive it everywhere.
sentences.chinese: 要是有一輛自備車該多好啊，我可以開車到處兜風。

definition: to (carry) on one's person/to (take) with one
to place an order/to book ahead
easily/without trouble/while one is at it/in passing/handy
